# AI safety

## Source of truth

Engine source > `GAME_MECHANICS.md` > README > AGENTS.md (process only).

## Forbidden

See `AGENTS.md` § Forbidden actions. Includes: git write, new deps, RNG outside `rng.ts`, UI rule duplication, bulk asset delete, cross-package renames.

## Migration

- `GameState` / types: shared → engine → web → docs (same task)
- `cards.json`: no id renames; JSON `type` is archetype
- `rng.ts` / reshuffle: tests or user waiver + repro

## Hallucination — verify before claiming

| Topic | File |
|-------|------|
| Events | `game-engine/src/round.ts` |
| Elections | `game-engine/src/round.ts` |
| Card asset/event | `game-engine/src/state.ts` |
| Audio paths | `apps/web/audio/soundManifest.ts` |

Say **unverified** if source not read.

## Uncertainty

Search engine → read mechanics doc → ask **one** question. Do not guess outcomes.

## Evidence

Never claim done without build. Cite file:line for behavior claims.

## Parallel agents

One writer per file. `shared` → `engine` → `web`.
